{"tid":1883392,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"翠華銅鑼灣旗艦店停業","createTime":"2020-02-17T02:19:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T05:34:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bf1e921e01e55f4f1d77147c51216df2783b109d","tid":1883392,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T02:19:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200217/XKPEDGSDGNPBUEDMLJUCIXG62M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200217%2FXKPEDGSDGNPBUEDMLJUCIXG62M%2F&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=b465fa7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200217%2FXKPEDGSDGNPBUEDMLJUCIXG62M%2F&h=1d0d4bba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200217/XKPEDGSDGNPBUEDMLJUCIXG62M/</a><br />\n<br />\n翠華銅鑼灣旗艦店停業<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】源自武漢的瘟疫對香港經濟造成沉重打擊，本港茶記一哥翠華集團，繼早前宣佈管理層減薪三成後，昨日再關閉其銅鑼灣旗艦店。位於駱克道、樓高三層的翠華餐廳昨日貼出告示，表示由於近日新型冠狀病毒肺炎日趨嚴重，為保障顧客及員工健康安全，決定即日起暫停營業，直至疫情受控為止。翠華表示，香港整體零售業正進入冰河時期，人流大幅減少及疫情仍未受控，集團需審視及調整目前餐廳網絡。<br />\n<br />\n另一餐飲連鎖集團616牛肉火鍋專門店亦宣告壯士斷臂。擁有20間分店的616昨日宣佈，即日起天后、北角、太子及新蒲崗四間分店需暫時停業，並需裁減四分一人手，現只望以外賣方式「捱生意」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200217/large/1581871871_0d64.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200217%2Flarge%2F1581871871_0d64.gif&h=3c93129f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n銅鑼灣駱克道翠華餐廳宣佈因疫情即日起暫停營業。黎樹雄攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n616火鍋店停開四舖<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：任職跨國建築師樓  全體員工留家一周<br />\n<br />\n616老闆程俊豪指，暫時停業的四間分店均是新開分店，其中新蒲崗更開業僅兩星期。他說，打邊爐家族集體感染個案後，大部份分店生意銳減至一成生意額，「北角店有三十幾張枱，有晚得一枱客，太子本身有四、五十張枱，就得四枱客」，大多分店星期一至四無生意，僅情人節當晚稍好，回復至四、五成生意額。<br />\n<br />\n616現時已裁減二十名員工，即四分一人手。程俊豪說，現時港人不欲外出用膳，且疫情仍未見頂，即使業主願意減租7%至12%，手上現金流亦只能「頂到四、五個月」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳詠恩"},{"pid":"472e6c3a34276783d0b2dec5f2951a547b2bbbb2","tid":1883392,"uid":147308,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T02:20:57.000Z","msg":"租太貴"},{"pid":"8c02e5c57b6e016ed882908ddb74ab83b58bc3ec","tid":1883392,"uid":35537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T02:22:40.000Z","msg":"咁撚難食，不意外"},{"pid":"f5c6fa354b68d0b35351e5ddd2ec2d076870714d","tid":1883392,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T02:25:45.000Z","msg":"616要支持，佢地麵同飯食好似"},{"pid":"424fe818d1721878c8ee0716fa33f3053b5944a5","tid":1883392,"uid":327462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T02:27:38.000Z","msg":"情人節去翠華食係咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7cc76ee5ae524194b77b3d51a76119f514569a5","tid":1883392,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"f5c6fa354b68d0b35351e5ddd2ec2d076870714d","tid":1883392,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T02:25:45.000Z","msg":"616要支持，佢地麵同飯食好似"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T02:30:31.000Z","msg":"616賣支那牛肉你食埋我果份"},{"pid":"7b9f3d38f89a79840302f398ea6e28d1c28c94a7","tid":1883392,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T02:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />垃圾摺埋都岩"},{"pid":"df817e29084efd8a081c3ef2e9c6f469ffd33917","tid":1883392,"uid":284668,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T02:56:12.000Z","msg":"垃圾翠華淨係做支那人生意，對香港人態度極差，又貴又難食，抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339f6c63f61c05da6edfe1c0f47f0e309717e63f","tid":1883392,"uid":74922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T03:11:01.000Z","msg":"翠華早執早着啦"},{"pid":"f1791a36e63ca27083db1f755a6714153f4f823b","tid":1883392,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T03:13:03.000Z","msg":"早死早超生"},{"pid":"ef4f25925460f97b29dd0b0b597b47ace8b81cf9","tid":1883392,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"